00:02:52.000 --> 00:03:00.000
After adding the beet, leave the soup to cook for another 15-20 minutes. 
Before removing from the heat, add the garlic.

00:03:15.000 --> 00:03:27.000
Everything will taste that bit better if the soup is left to stand... until tomorrow. Or at least for 2-3 hours.

